metadata.name: PAPA
metadata.description: The PAPA NFT collection is a set of unique digital collectibles that contribute directly to the growth of the PAPA Token. By minting a PAPA NFT, you become an essential part of our community and gain access to exclusive events, airdrops, and other perks. Each NFT also serves as a key to unlock participation in our innovative 'Feeding PAPA' feature. Own a one-of-a-kind PAPA NFT today and join us in shaping the future of PAPA!
